                and you do not need to go out and buy newspapers. And you can contact us when you encounter any problems in the website.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="img img-responsive" src="~/Content/desingimg/gggd.jpg" />
            </div>
        </div>
